OL,3,CPolice urge public not to spread
OL,4,Cmisinformation after Bootle incident
OL,6,FMerseyside Police have urged members
OL,7,Fof the public to avoid sharing rumours
OL,8,Fand misinformation following an
OL,9,Fincident involving a delivery driver
OL,10,Fand a large group of youths in Bootle
OL,11,Fon Friday evening.
OL,13,FThe incident occurred at around 6.50pm
OL,14,Fnear an alleyway off Edward Jenner
OL,15,FAvenue.
OL,17,FAccording to police, an independent
OL,18,Fwitness reported that a delivery
OL,19,Fdriver was riding his bicycle when he
OL,20,Fwas approached by a group of around 20
OL,21,Fyouths.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
