FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781970468
OL,3,CPolice urge public not to spread
OL,4,Cmisinformation after Bootle incident
OL,6,FThe group allegedly stopped the rider
OL,7,Fand grabbed hold of his bike as he
OL,8,Fattempted to continue his journey.
OL,10,FPolice said the driver tried to escape
OL,11,Fbut was then subjected to punches from
OL,12,Fmembers of the group. Officers stated
OL,13,Fthat the driver defended himself while
OL,14,Fcontinuing efforts to get away from
OL,15,Fthose involved.
OL,17,FWhen officers arrived at the scene,
OL,18,Fthey witnessed the youths behaving
OL,19,Faggressively, shouting at the driver
OL,20,Fand attempting to confront him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781970468
OL,3,CPolice urge public not to spread
OL,4,Cmisinformation after Bootle incident
OL,6,FFollowing enquiries, including
OL,7,Fevidence from an independent third-
OL,8,Fparty witness, detectives say they
OL,9,Fhave concluded that the youths had
OL,10,Fassaulted the delivery driver and that
OL,11,Fhe acted in self-defence.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Louise
OL,14,FBirchall said police were satisfied
OL,15,Fthe driver's actions were defensive
OL,16,Fand urged people not to share social
OL,17,Fmedia posts that create a "false
OL,18,Fnarrative" about what took place.
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
