OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781970468
OL,3,CPolice urge public not to spread
OL,4,Cmisinformation after Bootle incident
OL,6,FShe said: "We have carried out
OL,7,Fextensive enquiries to understand the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of what happened and can
OL,9,Fconfirm from an independent witness
OL,10,Fthat the delivery driver was defending
OL,11,Fhimself after being confronted by 20
OL,12,Fyouths.
OL,14,F"We are satisfied that he had acted in
OL,15,Fself-defence.
OL,17,F"We are aware that social media posts
OL,18,Fare circulating online and would urge
OL,19,Fpeople not to share rumours or
OL,20,Fmisinformation which creates a false
OL,21,Fnarrative of what actually took place."
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOUyD@AOU}D@gO]
